developed as a contiguous Industrial Development is 75.8 acres, while the remaining land has a variety of potential uses including industrial, commercial, retail, and multi-family. Located within the Scioto Darby Watershed, the largest portion of the site is 75.8 acres on the Western side of Alton Darby Creek Road with the remaining portion on the Eastern side. I-70 and I-270 are within minutes to the site via Feder Road and Hilliard Rome Road.
